{"id":835103243,"question_id":3,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"1 year, 7 months","timestamp":1667359999,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"6 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/835103243/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"44.5 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int lengthOfLongestSubstring(String s) {\n        int[] arr = new int[256];\n        \n        Arrays.fill(arr, -1);\n        \n        int st=0, max=0;\n        for(int i=0; i<s.length(); i++){\n            char c  = s.charAt(i);\n            \n            if(arr[c]>=0){\n                st = Math.max(st, arr[c]+1);\n            }\n            max = Math.max(max, i-st+1);\n            arr[c] = i;\n        }\n        \n        \n        \n        return max;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
